[
  {
    "text": "Andi: Technology can be\na great way",
    "start": 0.166,
    "duration": 1.569
  },
  {
    "text": "to stay in touch\nwith family and friends.",
    "start": 1.735,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "But when you rely on this",
    "start": 3.737,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "as the only way\nto communicate...",
    "start": 5.372,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, you can text.\nThat's what we do.",
    "start": 6.74,
    "duration": 2.369
  },
  {
    "text": "But then aren't\nall your conversations",
    "start": 9.109,
    "duration": 3.069
  },
  {
    "text": "just staring at your phone?",
    "start": 12.178,
    "duration": 2.102
  },
  {
    "text": "...you could\nreally be missing out.",
    "start": 14.28,
    "duration": 1.736
  },
  {
    "text": "You should learn\nsign language.",
    "start": 16.016,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "I know, I know,\nbut what did she say?",
    "start": 17.35,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "That is what she said.",
    "start": 18.752,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "We might all\ncommunicate differently...",
    "start": 20.52,
    "duration": 2.102
  },
  {
    "text": "- Andi Shack.\n- ...but what's most important",
    "start": 22.622,
    "duration": 1.935
  },
  {
    "text": "is to make the connection.",
    "start": 24.557,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Will you teach me\nsign language?",
    "start": 25.725,
    "duration": 4.305
  },
  {
    "text": "Because when we see\neach other face to face...",
    "start": 30.03,
    "duration": 2.435
  },
  {
    "text": "I like you.",
    "start": 32.465,
    "duration": 2.603
  },
  {
    "text": "I like you, too.",
    "start": 35.068,
    "duration": 3.337
  },
  {
    "text": "Too.",
    "start": 38.405,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "Too.",
    "start": 40.14,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "...then we can truly",
    "start": 41.141,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "be seen and heard.",
    "start": 42.375,
    "duration": 1.669
  }
]